summary: This code defines the class AICMVNodeBase, which is a subclass of AIAlgNodeBase. It has three properties: urgentTo_p (a pointer to the urgent value), delta_p (a pointer to the change value), and foPorts (an array of forwarding ports). The class also includes a brief description and notes for future improvements.
